Liverpool Kop End【高普：我想謝拉特接我棒！】<br />
高普接受英國 The Times 訪問（都幾詳盡，有時間譯畀大家睇），表示「假如他日我離開（利物浦）或球隊解僱我，我不會太在意誰會接任，但我希望會是謝拉特。我會確保我給予他所有他需要的資訊。」<br />
&ldquo;I told him when I leave, or the club sack me, I don&rsquo;t care of course who&rsquo;ll be my successor, but I&rsquo;d love that he&rsquo;d be it. I&rsquo;ll do everything I can to make sure he gets all the information he needs.&ldquo;

Klopp: &quot;We have 73pts, chance to get 76pts, in a difficult season with a lot of competitors.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;After Sunday we have a long flight to Australia so then I'll think about everything.&quot;
